'''{{PAGENAME}}''' (ヴォルカノン ''Vorukanon'') is a [[:Category:Characters (RF4)|character]] in ''[[Rune Factory 4]]''.

==Profile==
===Personality===
Volkanon is a top-notch butler. He is very responsible and passionated with his job. He acts caring and rather melodramatic, not afraid to shed a tear that is.

With his awesome brute strength and expert craftsmanship capability, he always try to make Lest/Frey's journey easier for example like clearing the giants logs blocking the paths in the woods and building a very impressive bridge out of scratch very swiftly and professionally.

Volkanon is very confident and proud to be able to assist in any way he can. He says "I can build bridges in my sleep, I assure you. It's no harder for me to put on pants!"

===Appearance===
Volkanon has light skin and blue eyes. His gray hair is styled neatly with a matching beard.

==Story==
A top-notch butler who serves the Native Wind Dragon, [[Ventuswill]]. Volkanon is capable of superhuman feats of strength, stating that it is only part of his duty as a butler. He is also allergic to flowers and regrets that he can't take care of them.

Later in the game, it is possible to unlock a feature that lets him be able to join the player's party when he/she has reached 2500 tourists.

==Events==
{{Main|Town Events (RF4)}}

==Requests==
There are no Requests in ''Rune Factory 4''.

==Relationships==
He always appears to [[Lest and Frey|Lest/Frey]] to assist in their matter even though they were not aware of it yet.

