==Trivia==
*He shares his birthday with [[Danny]] from [[Rune Factory: Frontier]] and [[Pia]] from [[Rune Factory 3: A Fantasy Harvest Moon|Rune Factory 3]].
*Volkanon built a bridge for Lest/Frey to pass across to reach Obsidian Mansion, similar with how Daria built(rebuilt) the bridge at Privera Forest for him (Micah) to get to the Racoon.
*After the player is married, regardless of what the protagonist's sex is, Volkanon will always address them as Sir [name].
